        provinces of Viet Nam
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients from both sexes, aged 18 years or older

          -  Patients complaining of symptoms consistent with reflux disease

